---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Wellness Retreats"
  description="Immersive multi-day wellness retreats to reset, reconnect, and transform in Hanalei Bay, Kauai."
>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <span class="page-hero__eyebrow">Signature Offerings</span>
    <h1 class="page-hero__heading">Wellness Retreats</h1>
    <span class="page-hero__rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <p class="page-hero__body">
      Immersive retreats and immersions to reset, reconnect, and transform.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="offering-detail">
    <div class="offering-detail__inner">

      <div class="offering-detail__image" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="offering-detail__content">
        <span class="u-label">About This Service</span>

        <p class="offering-detail__body">
          Nestled in the emerald valleys and sacred waters of Hanalei Bay, our wellness
          retreats are multi-day immersive journeys that weave together our full spectrum
          of healing modalities into a coherent, transformational arc — designed for
          deep reset, lasting change, and spiritual reconnection.
        </p>
        <p class="offering-detail__body">
          Each retreat is small and intentionally curated, combining daily bodywork,
          energy medicine, sound healing, botanical nourishment, movement, and guided
          inner work in one of the most spiritually powerful places on earth.
        </p>

        <ul class="offering-detail__benefits" aria-label="Benefits">
          <li class="offering-detail__benefit">Complete nervous system reset and stress liberation</li>
          <li class="offering-detail__benefit">Multi-modal healing across body, mind, and spirit</li>
          <li class="offering-detail__benefit">Deep community connection in a sacred container</li>
          <li class="offering-detail__benefit">Tools and practices to sustain transformation at home</li>
          <li class="offering-detail__benefit">Immersion in the healing energy of Kauai</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">
          <a href="/booking/" class="btn btn--primary">Enquire About Retreats</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="page-cta" aria-labelledby="retreat-cta">
    <div class="page-cta__inner">
      <h2 class="page-cta__heading" id="retreat-cta">Explore more offerings</h2>
      <p class="page-cta__body">Elevated Healing. Lasting Transformation.</p>
      <a href="/offerings/" class="btn btn--outline">View All Services</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
